{"word":"περίειμι 1","slug":"περίειμι 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n81297\" key=\"peri/eimi1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">περίειμι</orth> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰμί</foreign> sum) <sense id=\"n81297.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be around</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">χωρίον ᾧ κύκλῳ τειχίον περιῆν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:81\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.81</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; but more freq. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n81297.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be superior to</tr_> another, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">surpass, excel</tr_>, c.gen.pers., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τόσσον ἐγὼ περί τ᾽ εἰμὶ θεῶν περί τ᾽ εἴμ᾽ ἀνθρώπων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:8:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.8.27</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1342.tlg001:113\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Emp.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">113</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:146\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.146</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:7:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mem.\">Mem.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIfor